title: [DBTech] vBArcade v2.0.2pl1 Branding Free
description:
Lite Branding Free Key = vbdude

vBArcade is a professional modular flash arcade game system. Easily converts your old favorites, and finds thousands more with the click of a button.

Highlights
This new modern arcade uses AJAX to enhance the playing experience and encourage users to compete both locally and globally among participating sites. Streamlined import and editing managers put games from mochi, armor, kongregate, v3arcade, ibproarcade and more into your arcade with ease. Fine-tuned access and scoring tools allow you to keep competition fresh and exciting, as well as social network tools to bring new users in to your site!



Current Version: v2.0.2pl1
Release Date: 11th May 2015
Forum Version: vBulletin 4.x.x
